      <div type="page" n="ix">
        <pb n="ix"/>
        <lg xml:id="block_A" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2Fa3f6fae8-9ac8-4a8b-9632-93d6a9941699.jp2/854,400,3710,1501/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>The desert mishkan was a portable sanctuary. Its care was guarded by the Levites and</l>
          <l>the priests yet it invited all to bring their offerings. Today, we are all caretakers of</l>
          <l>Mishkan T&apos;filah; may our offerings be acceptable before God.</l>
          <l>May all who enter find joy, solace and meaning.</l>
          <l>RABBI ELYSE D. FRISHMAN</l>
          <l>Editor</l>
          <l>RABBI PETER S. KNOBEL</l>
          <l>Chair of the Editorial Committee</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
